Run package executables

USAGE:
    ir tool run [Rscript-options...] [--with <pkg>]... [--r-version <spec>] --from <pkg-ref> <command> [args...]
    ir tool run [Rscript-options...] [--with <pkg>]... [--r-version <spec>] <pkg-ref> [args...]

COMMANDS:
    run  Resolve a package and run an executable from its exec directory

ENVIRONMENT:
    IR_CACHE_DIR   override the cache dir (default: tools::R_user_dir("ir", "cache"))
    IR_RSCRIPT     path to the Rscript executable (default: Rscript on PATH)
